{"tid":1832840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紐西蘭旅遊巴士翻覆 至少20名中國旅客受傷","createTime":"2020-01-21T12:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T12:49:26.000Z","uid":226739,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f96af82bab055f3e066e84194840d860445e7542","tid":1832840,"uid":226739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/01/21/phpheuK0l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2FphpheuK0l.jpg&h=23133a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭旅遊巴士翻覆 至少20名中國旅客受傷<br />\n    <br />\n 一輛巴士在紐西蘭皇后鎮附近的道路翻覆，造成車上中國旅遊團至少20人受傷，其中2人重傷。（畫面擷取自紐西蘭電視一臺TVNZ 1）<br />\n2020-01-21 17:31:30<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一輛巴士在紐西蘭皇后鎮（Queenstown）附近的道路翻覆，造成車上中國旅遊團至少20人受傷，其中2人重傷，被送往醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，今日（21日）約下午1點，一輛旅遊巴士翻覆在皇后鎮通往格萊諾基（Glenorchy）的道路上，造成至少20人受傷，現場指揮官證實，所有傷者皆是中國遊客。<br />\n<br />\n當局派出2架直升機和3輛救護車到場救治，有2名中國遊客重傷送醫，事故路段估計下午8點恢復通車，而事故原因仍在調查當中。有目擊者表示，巴士翻覆地點是一處急轉彎，視野不好，以前也曾發生過交通事故，但通常是在冬季。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3046842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3046842&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7ca7555a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3046842&h=bd1f8954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3046842</a>"},{"pid":"799922d183a4e16d5fdfc827902f76e3c51beaf2","tid":1832840,"uid":226739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"我唔要中國人受傷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d002c84ef009c30c0674fa99a06015034a0832c","tid":1832840,"uid":226739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:24:59.000Z","msg":"我唔係要呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" cl